%% Data Science Pipelines Tekton - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SDK Client
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant UI as ds-pipeline-ui<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant API as ds-pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP | 8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP
    participant S3 as S3/Minio<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Tekton as Tekton Controller
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SW as Scheduled Workflow Controller
    participant Cache as cache-server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc-server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Envoy as metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC-Web
    participant MW as metadata-writer

    Note over User, Tekton: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>OAuth: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS TLS, OAuth Token
    OAuth->>UI: Forward (HTTP localhost)<br/>Proxied identity
    UI->>API: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTP, kubeflow-userid header
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL 3306, Username/Password
    API->>S3: Upload pipeline artifacts<br/>HTTP 9000, AccessKey/SecretKey
    API->>K8s: Create Tekton PipelineRun<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA Token
    K8s->>Tekton: Schedule PipelineRun
    Tekton-->>K8s: PipelineRun status updates

    Note over PA, API: Flow 2: Pipeline Run Status Persistence

    PA->>K8s: Watch PipelineRuns/TaskRuns<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA Token
    K8s-->>PA: PipelineRun status events
    PA->>API: Update run status<br/>HTTP 8888, SA identity

    Note over SW, K8s: Flow 3: Scheduled Workflow Execution

    SW->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA Token
    K8s-->>SW: ScheduledWorkflow events
    SW->>K8s: Create PipelineRun (on schedule)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA Token

    Note over K8s, Cache: Flow 4: Task Caching

    K8s->>Cache: TaskRun admission webhook<br/>HTTPS TLS (webhook certs)
    Cache->>DB: Check cache<br/>MySQL 3306, Username/Password
    DB-->>Cache: Cache result
    Cache-->>K8s: Mutated TaskRun (cached or proceed)

    Note over MW, MLMD: Flow 5: ML Metadata

    MW->>MLMD: Write run metadata<br/>gRPC 8080, cluster-internal
    MLMD->>DB: Store metadata<br/>MySQL 3306, Username/Password
    UI->>Envoy: Query metadata<br/>HTTP gRPC-Web 9090
    Envoy->>MLMD: Forward gRPC<br/>gRPC 8080
    MLMD-->>Envoy: Metadata response
    Envoy-->>UI: gRPC-Web response
